parameters:
\n<Rui>It's obviously a monster. Are you one of the
embodiments of despair?

\n<Rui>...Nothing but vile monsters until the very end.
Fine, bring it on!

\n<Mansion's Monster>Woman"...Gehihihi, it feels good to be back,
female hole"
\n<Rui>...I won't lose so easily again. Be prepared!

A beautifully decorated key lies where the monster
was.
